{"type": "article", "id": 14410, "title": "了解这 9 个拍照小技巧，就能拍出好看的城市照", "description": "摄影是光影的艺术。", "date": "2015-09-08T17:45:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 26, "name": "instagram"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 831, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105331RLp4lUIweXofhOsJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t很多人都说玩摄影并没有什么固定的规则，毕竟牵扯到审美众口难调。特别是到了<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://instagram.com/jayscale\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> 的时代，还有照片比加一个滤镜更带感的吗？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t科技也许让人类变懒惰了。就说构图，<span>如之前的</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://instagram.com/jayscale\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a><span> 只规定上传方形照片。就好像有人拎着你的耳朵不停念叨：构图请注意黄金分割线。所以拍出来的照片也不会太差吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不过，话又说回来，那些酷炫滤镜的背后还是对光影、色温、曝光度、色调的利用，所以要真的拍好照片，真的还得走点心。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这里有 10 个在 <a href=\"http://instagram.com/jayscale\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> 以拍城市而著名的摄影师——<a href=\"http://instagram.com/jayscale/\" target=\"_blank\">@jayscale</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/visionelie/\" target=\"_blank\">@visionelie</a> ( <a href=\"http://instagram.com/whateverelie/\" target=\"_blank\">@whateverelie</a>)，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/stevesweatpants/\" target=\"_blank\">@stevesweatpants</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/ecolephoto/\" target=\"_blank\">@ecolephoto</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/alinatsvor/\" target=\"_blank\">@alinatsvor</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/black_soap/\" target=\"_blank\">@black_soap</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/13thwitness/\" target=\"_blank\">@13thwitness</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/ryanmillier/\" target=\"_blank\">@ryanmillier</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/1st/\" target=\"_blank\">@1st</a>，<a href=\"http://instagram.com/trashhand/\" target=\"_blank\">@trashhand</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t他们谈了谈如何才能拍出<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://instagram.com/jayscale\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> 风格的城市摄影。哦，对了，虽然他们也偶尔使用 iPhone 拍摄，但专业相机仍然是拍摄城市的好帮手。毕竟如果阳光不够灿烂，手机可没有大光圈的效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105325fCyhu3ESDWMjqod7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105325y103qsclJ9Imf5MO.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105326ZNPIkUE90nWl4A7u.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210532657UGFe8maSE3Ly1b.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021053277WZf2JC9m0Yauwcv.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105328RmJ6C4Du0rX1WlP5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t以下是他们的拍摄小秘籍，包括使用的相机、光圈和快门速度，以及后期剪辑喜欢用的软件：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t1.  喜欢用大光圈。不要低于 1.8 或者 2.0 。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t2. 最喜欢的修图软件是：电脑上可以 <a href=\"http://lightroom.adobe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Adobe Lightroom</a>，手机上 <a href=\"http://vsco.co/vscocam\" target=\"_blank\">VSCO Cam</a><span style=\"text-align:start;\">，</span><a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/app/snapseed/id439438619?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">Snapseed</a>，<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/slow-shutter-cam/id357404131?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">Slow Shutter</a>。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t3.  有专业的器材，比不过，也用 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">iPhone 拍摄。</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">iPhone 是用得最多的手机拍摄工具。<span style=\"text-align:start;\">@ecolephoto 说，还有比 iP</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">hone 更容易控制曝光的相机嘛？</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t4.  在所有自用的相机中，有<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.usa.canon.com/cusa/consumer/products/cameras/slr_cameras/eos_5d_mark_iii\" target=\"_blank\">Canon EOS 5D Mark III</a>，<a href=\"http://www.usa.canon.com/cusa/support/consumer/eos_slr_camera_systems/eos_35mm_slr_cameras/eos_3\" target=\"_blank\">Canon EOS-3</a>，也有<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.sony.com/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras/ilce-7m2-body-kit\" target=\"_blank\">Sony α7 II</a> 。这些摄影师也会选择机身更轻便的。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span><span>@stevesweatpants 说，他选择</span><span> </span><a href=\"http://www.sony.com/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras/ilce-7m2-body-kit\" target=\"_blank\">Sony α7 II</a> 主要是因为纽约太大了，带着它出行更方便。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span>5. </span><span> 最常使用的专业相机有：</span><a href=\"http://www.usa.canon.com/cusa/consumer/products/cameras/slr_cameras/eos_5d_mark_iii\" target=\"_blank\">Canon EOS 5D MarkIII</a>，<span>a </span><a href=\"http://www.usa.canon.com/cusa/consumer/products/cameras/slr_cameras/eos_1d_x\" target=\"_blank\">Canon EOS-1D X</a>，<span>a </span><a href=\"http://en.leica-camera.com/Photography/Leica-M/Leica-M-P\" target=\"_blank\">Leica M-P 240</a><span>，</span><span>RX100，</span><a href=\"http://en.leica-camera.com/Photography/Compact-Cameras/Leica-D-Lux-Typ-109\" target=\"_blank\">Leica D-Lux</a>，<a href=\"http://www.usa.canon.com/cusa/consumer/products/cameras/slr_cameras/eos_6d\" target=\"_blank\">Canon EOS 6D</a>，<a href=\"http://www.nikonusa.com/en/Nikon-Products/Product-Archive/dslr-cameras/D800.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nikon D800 D-SLR</a>，<span> </span><a href=\"http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x_t10/\" target=\"_blank\">Fujifilm X-T10</a>。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span>6.  因为是拍城市景色，有时候也带上遮光罩。通常大光圈</span><span> f 2.8 - f 5.6 带着遮光器。如果要拍一个路过的行人 ，通常来说，会用高速快门，光圈在</span><span> </span><span>f 4，这样光圈和快门的配合可以捕捉到周围更多细节。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t7.  通常来说，拍摄城市需要保证一定的清晰度和锐度。所以可以在强光下用“曝光不足”1 - 2 档。\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span>8.  如果在晚上去拍摄城市，就需要时间曝光长。</span><span>感光度在 100 左右。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>9.  如果背着专业相机扫街，</span><a href=\"http://www.sony.com/electronics/cyber-shot-compact-cameras/dsc-rx100\" target=\"_blank\">Sony RX100</a> <span>也许是个不错的选择。小巧，因为没有人会注意到它的存在。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021053283mIxCpSVTXuhZGtr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1047\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.96944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210532962vTYB3lUwSpWQDa.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1031\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.95462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105329zuIRB9bry2NnjZw3.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1049\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"0.9712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105330ulnCk3o9jeztva17.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1091\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.01018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105330gPrnCkWyZHBiIeS7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1282\" title=\"。。\" alt=\"。。\" data-ratio=\"1.18703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}